dibabel-diff-content--login-error: In right to left languages, it's "upper left".
dibabel-filters-groupby--placeholder: A placeholder on a dropdown. Possible values: by language, by wiki, etc.
dibabel-header-beta--label: Appears next to the logo at the top. {{Identical|Beta}}
dibabel-header-description: A title at the top of the page. $1 is replaced by a link to the Wikimedia user page of the tool's author.
dibabel-header-links--bugs: A link at the top of the page. Links to [https://github.com/nyurik/dibabel-js/issues issue tracking on GitHub].
dibabel-header-links--help: A link at the top of the page. Links to [[:mw:Multilingual Templates and Modules]].
dibabel-header-links--source: A link at the top of the page. Links to [https://github.com/nyurik/dibabel-js the source code of the tool on GitHub].
dibabel-language-unknown: Describes an unknown language, in the Language menu ({{msg-dibabel|Dibabel-dibabel-filters-lang}}).
dibabel-table-cell-diverged--tooltip: $1 pages have local modifications and must be synchronized individually.
dibabel-table-cell-outdated--tooltip: $1 pages are behind the primary and can be synchronized automatically.
dibabel-table-cell-status--diverged-labe: A status indicator in the table.
dibabel-table-cell-status--diverged-tool: Tooltip for the icon next to {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-dibabel-table-cell-status--diverged-label}}
dibabel-table-cell-status--ok--tooltip: Tooltip for the icon next to {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-dibabel-table-cell-status--ok-label}}
dibabel-table-cell-status--ok-label:
'''This is not an OK button!'''

A status indicator in the table.

It should probably be the same as {{msg-dibabel|Dibabel-dibabel-filters-status-ok}}.
dibabel-table-cell-status--outdated-labe: A status indicator in the table. $1 is the number of revisions.
dibabel-table-cell-status--outdated-link: Show what changed in the last $1 revisions of the primary $2 in a new tab.
dibabel-table-cell-status--outdated-tool: Tooltip for the icon next to {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-dibabel-table-cell-status--outdated-label}}
dibabel-table-cell-status--unlocalized-l: A status indicator in the table.
dibabel-table-cell-status--unlocalized-t: Tooltip for the icon next to {{msg-dibabel|dibabel-dibabel-table-cell-status--unlocalized-label}}
dibabel-table-cell-unlocalized--tooltip: $1 pages are identical to the original. These pages need to be localized because some dependent templates may have different names on that wiki. This can be done automatically.
dibabel-table-header-wikipage--link: Tooltip for the icon next to a link in a table. $1 and $2 are page titles.
dibabel-table-icons-protection--rights: Tooltip for a lock icon on a row.
dibabel-table-icons-protection--tooltip: Tooltip for a lock icon at the top of the table.
